---
import { siteConfig } from '../../data/siteConfig';
---

<section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 bg-mesh-ink overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-fine opacity-40"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Image left - rounded with shadow -->
      <div class="reveal-scale relative">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/fotos-jd-infra/fotos jd infra/DJI_0004-1024x576.jpg.jpeg"
            alt="Bedrijfspand JD Infra drone"
            class="w-full aspect-[16/10] object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Floating glass stat badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 right-4 sm:right-8 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 hidden sm:block z-10 shadow-2xl border border-white/15">
          <span class="block font-heading font-semibold text-4xl text-accent-300" data-counter="2006" data-counter-type="year">2006</span>
          <span class="text-white/60 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-heading mt-1 block">Opgericht</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content right -->
      <div class="reveal relative">
        <span class="section-num absolute -top-14 sm:-top-20 -left-2 !text-white !opacity-10">05</span>
        <span class="eyebrow mb-6 relative !text-accent-300">Over ons</span>
        <h2 class="display-lg text-white mb-6 relative">
          Een Zeeuws bedrijf met <span class="accent-serif !text-accent-300">karakter</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-white/70 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          JD Infra aannemingsbedrijf is in 2006 opgericht en in de loop van de jaren uitgegroeid tot een vakkundig infrabedrijf met 12 tot 15 vaste medewerkers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          In maart 2018 zijn wij verhuisd naar ons nieuwe bedrijfspand op industrieterrein Karreveld te Koudekerke. Van hieruit bedienen wij heel Zeeland.
        </p>

        <!-- Stats row - open, no boxes -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-10 gap-y-5 mb-10">
          <div>
            <span class="block font-heading font-semibold text-3xl text-white">20</span>
            <span class="text-white/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-heading">Jaar ervaring</span>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:border-l border-white/15 sm:pl-10">
            <span class="block font-heading font-semibold text-3xl text-white">12-15</span>
            <span class="text-white/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-heading">Vakmensen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:border-l border-white/15 sm:pl-10">
            <span class="block font-heading font-semibold text-3xl text-white">Zeeland</span>
            <span class="text-white/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-heading">Werkgebied</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/over-ons/" class="editorial-link text-white hover:text-accent-300 border-white/40 hover:border-accent-300">
          Lees ons verhaal
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
